body: It seemed somewhat non-trivial to create a separate Travis-CI matrix for testing the Docker image, it would likely require making separate scripts for what Travis currently does and another for testing Docker container, and I'm not sure how you want this to be done, so I didn't do it. --- This change is [](https://reviewable.io/reviews/toktok/apidsl/22)
